<p />
<h3><a name="Cost"></a> Cost </h3>
<p />
There is no registration fee for this workshop, but you must fill out the <font color="#ff0000"> <strong>&gt;&gt;&gt; <a href="http://indico.fnal.gov/confRegistrationFormDisplay.py?confId=2241" target="_top">registration form</a> &gt;&gt;&gt;</strong> </font><br>
Limited travel support is available for qualified individuals. You can indicate your need on the application page.
<p />
<p />
<h3><a name="Location"></a> Location </h3>
<a href="http://www.clemson.edu/" target="_top">Clemson University</a> campus.
Meeting room: room 116 in the CS building ( <span class="twikiNewLink">McAdams<a href="/bin/edit/Education/McAdams?topicparent=Education.GSAW09" rel="nofollow" title="McAdams (this topic does not yet exist; you can create it)">?</a></span> building )
<p />
<h3><a name="Transportation_and_Directions"></a> Transportation and Directions </h3>
A campus map is at: <a href="http://www.clemson.edu/campusmap/" target="_top">http://www.clemson.edu/campusmap/</a>
<p />
The closest airport is Greeenville-Spartanburg (GSP). Another option is Atlanta, ATL which is
2 hours away by car. 
<p />
Shuttle services are available for both airports. (please check GSP airport for more information)
<p />
