<p />
Note: the workshop is collocated with <a href="http://www.cs.clemson.edu/acmse09/" target="_top">ACMSE09</a>
<h3><a name="Sponsors"></a> Sponsors </h3>
The workshop is supported by <a href="http://opensciencegrid.org" target="_top">Open Science Grid</a>, through the support of the <a href="http://www.er.doe.gov/" target="_top">Department of Energy Office of Science</a> and the <a href="http://nsf.gov" target="_top">National Science Foundation</a>.
